# module: eng.cache
# status: planned
# purpose: reproducible cache keys, pinned downloads, fixture mode, and hit/miss artifacts.
#
# Current implementation:
#   no native cache module yet. Cache behavior must be expressed by explicit
#   files, hashes, and reviewable process or read boundaries.
#
# Planned helper vocabulary:
#   cache key from ...
#   cache get
#   cache put
#   require hash
#
# Review contract:
#   cache key, source, expected hash, observed hash, hit/miss status, profile
#   policy, and source span.
#
# Non-goal:
#   implicit caching is not acceptable for engineering review. Cache use must
#   be visible in review/runtime artifacts.
